00:46:45,599 --> 00:46:47,960
[SPEAKER_00] različitim opijatima.

725
00:46:47,960 --> 00:46:50,179
[SPEAKER_00] Još dan danas

726
00:46:50,179 --> 00:46:50,880
[SPEAKER_00] nisu ispunjeni.

727
00:46:50,880 --> 00:46:54,320
[SPEAKER_00] A drugi primjer,

728
00:46:54,320 --> 00:46:56,380
[SPEAKER_00] malo južnije iz regije,

729
00:46:56,380 --> 00:46:58,420
[SPEAKER_00] je Međugorje.

730
00:46:58,420 --> 00:47:00,920
[SPEAKER_00] Prije ukazanja,

731
00:47:00,920 --> 00:47:01,380
[SPEAKER_00] isto to,

732
00:47:01,380 --> 00:47:03,219
[SPEAKER_00] nakon ukazanja

733
00:47:03,219 --> 00:47:04,119
[SPEAKER_00] vijerski turizam.

734
00:47:08,619 --> 00:47:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] Pouzdanost gradi naš karakter.

735
00:47:10,960 --> 00:47:13,960
[SPEAKER_00] Da se znamo

736
00:47:13,960 --> 00:47:15,579
[SPEAKER_00] oduprijed tom duhu materializma.

737
00:47:15,579 --> 00:47:17,659
[SPEAKER_00] Da se znamo

738
00:47:17,659 --> 00:47:19,079
[SPEAKER_00] oduprijed tom duhu pogleda.

739
00:47:19,079 --> 00:47:28,360
[SPEAKER_00] I da se znamo

740
00:47:28,360 --> 00:47:29,179
[SPEAKER_00] bogatiti u Bogu.

741
00:47:29,179 --> 00:47:36,460
[SPEAKER_00] Pitanje koje se postavilo

742
00:47:36,460 --> 00:47:37,280
[SPEAKER_00] u najavi je

743
00:47:37,280 --> 00:47:39,039
[SPEAKER_00] je li novac dobar

744
00:47:39,039 --> 00:47:39,539
[SPEAKER_00] ili loš?

745
00:47:39,539 --> 00:47:41,079
[SPEAKER_00] Kada smo kod toga,

746
00:47:41,079 --> 00:47:42,099
[SPEAKER_00] hoćemo li odgovoriti?

747
00:47:42,099 --> 00:47:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Novac je neutralan, da.

748
00:47:46,000 --> 00:47:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, niti je dobar,

749
00:47:49,000 --> 00:47:49,679
[SPEAKER_00] niti je loš.

750
00:47:49,679 --> 00:47:52,579
[SPEAKER_00] Bitno je kako ga mi koristimo.

751
00:47:52,579 --> 00:47:55,739
[SPEAKER_00] A kako će vam mi koristiti?

752
00:47:55,739 --> 00:47:57,719
[SPEAKER_00] Ovisi o našem karakteru.

753
00:47:57,719 --> 00:47:59,440
[SPEAKER_00] Kako izgradimo naš karakter?

754
00:47:59,440 --> 00:48:05,679
[SPEAKER_00] I na kraju,

755
00:48:07,280 --> 00:48:10,079
[SPEAKER_00] kod ovog podnaslova,

756
00:48:10,079 --> 00:48:11,460
[SPEAKER_00] naša odgovornosti,

757
00:48:11,460 --> 00:48:14,159
[SPEAKER_00] biti pouzdan stvara zadovoljstvo.

758
00:48:14,159 --> 00:48:16,320
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

759
00:48:16,320 --> 00:48:18,079
[SPEAKER_00] ako razlikujemo Božju odgovornost

760
00:48:18,079 --> 00:48:20,099
[SPEAKER_00] i našu odgovornost,

761
00:48:20,099 --> 00:48:22,139
[SPEAKER_00] te vjerno isponjavamo ono

762
00:48:22,139 --> 00:48:23,260
[SPEAKER_00] što je naša odgovornost,

763
00:48:23,260 --> 00:48:25,380
[SPEAKER_00] na kraju možemo biti zadovoljni.

764
00:48:28,480 --> 00:48:29,420
[SPEAKER_00] Pazite samo,

765
00:48:29,420 --> 00:48:32,320
[SPEAKER_00] tu može doći do sotanskog privida.

766
00:48:32,320 --> 00:48:34,760
[SPEAKER_00] U smislu,

767
00:48:34,760 --> 00:48:36,599
[SPEAKER_00] neko će reći,

768
00:48:36,599 --> 00:48:38,039
[SPEAKER_00] ja jesam dobar upravitelj,

769
00:48:38,039 --> 00:48:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] dobro upravljam

770
00:48:39,000 --> 00:48:42,659
[SPEAKER_00] i učinit ću neku stvar za sebe,

771
00:48:42,659 --> 00:48:44,679
[SPEAKER_00] nešto ono,

772
00:48:44,679 --> 00:48:46,420
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam,

773
00:48:46,420 --> 00:48:47,280
[SPEAKER_00] ajde, sad ću reći,

774
00:48:47,280 --> 00:48:48,920
[SPEAKER_00] žene će,

775
00:48:48,920 --> 00:48:51,400
[SPEAKER_00] počati će se sa nejakim cipelama,

776
00:48:51,679 --> 00:48:52,900
[SPEAKER_00] a muškarci će

777
00:48:52,900 --> 00:48:55,719
[SPEAKER_00] kupit tenesice.

778
00:48:55,719 --> 00:49:00,039
[SPEAKER_00] I mi mislimo,

779
00:49:00,039 --> 00:49:01,320
[SPEAKER_00] ovo je sad banalan primjer,

780
00:49:01,320 --> 00:49:02,519
[SPEAKER_00] ima puno većih,

781
00:49:02,519 --> 00:49:03,579
[SPEAKER_00] puno viših

782
00:49:03,579 --> 00:49:06,940
[SPEAKER_00] većih primjera od toga,

783
00:49:06,940 --> 00:49:08,500
[SPEAKER_00] ali ajmo se držati na ovom banalnom

784
00:49:08,500 --> 00:49:09,519
[SPEAKER_00] da ne prozovimo nekoga.

785
00:49:09,519 --> 00:49:12,099
[SPEAKER_00] I mi mislimo da smo,

786
00:49:12,099 --> 00:49:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] radeći puno,

787
00:49:13,000 --> 00:49:13,900
[SPEAKER_00] radeći dobro,

788
00:49:13,900 --> 00:49:16,579
[SPEAKER_00] to zaslužili za sebe.

789
00:49:16,579 --> 00:49:18,619
[SPEAKER_00] Kad smo zaslužili,

790
00:49:18,619 --> 00:49:19,179
[SPEAKER_00] sad, odmah,

791
00:49:19,179 --> 00:49:20,340
[SPEAKER_00] posaću ću se to kupit,

792
00:49:20,340 --> 00:49:23,960
[SPEAKER_00] nekad to može biti

793
00:49:23,960 --> 00:49:25,119
[SPEAKER_00] neprijateljava zamka,

794
00:49:25,119 --> 00:49:26,380
[SPEAKER_00] gdje,

795
00:49:26,380 --> 00:49:28,420
[SPEAKER_00] ako ste odredili nešto za sebe,

796
00:49:28,420 --> 00:49:30,420
[SPEAKER_00] ako ste odredili nešto s roditeljima

797
00:49:30,420 --> 00:49:31,719
[SPEAKER_00] i dogovorili sa roditeljima

798
00:49:31,719 --> 00:49:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] da nećete sad uzimati to i to,

799
00:49:34,000 --> 00:49:35,360
[SPEAKER_00] jer ste dogovorili sa ženom

800
00:49:35,360 --> 00:49:36,860
[SPEAKER_00] da nećete uzimati to i to,

801
00:49:36,860 --> 00:49:38,539
[SPEAKER_00] i vi to ipak napravite,

802
00:49:38,539 --> 00:49:38,840
[SPEAKER_00] zašto?

803
00:49:38,840 --> 00:49:39,800
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što ste zaslužili,

804
00:49:39,800 --> 00:49:45,039
[SPEAKER_00] kasnije to može unijet nemir.

805
00:49:45,039 --> 00:49:47,260
[SPEAKER_00] Možete se posvađati zbog toga

806
00:49:47,260 --> 00:49:48,440
[SPEAKER_00] i

807
00:49:48,440 --> 00:49:51,119
[SPEAKER_00] doživjeti nekakav neslat

808
00:49:51,119 --> 00:49:52,280
[SPEAKER_00] u vašem životu?

809
00:49:52,280 --> 00:49:54,039
[SPEAKER_00] I ovak se mislite,

810
00:49:54,039 --> 00:49:55,719
[SPEAKER_00] a samo sam si htio kupiti to.

811
00:49:55,719 --> 00:49:57,420
[SPEAKER_00] Zaslužio sam.

812
00:49:57,420 --> 00:49:59,400
[SPEAKER_00] Zaslužila sam.

813
00:50:04,059 --> 00:50:05,719
[SPEAKER_00] evo moj jedan pozitivan primjer.

814
00:50:05,719 --> 00:50:08,579
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam se oženio,

815
00:50:08,579 --> 00:50:13,559
[SPEAKER_00] žena i ja smo živeli u dvadesetak kvadrata

816
00:50:13,559 --> 00:50:16,159
[SPEAKER_00] i odlučili smo da nećemo ići nigdje

817
00:50:16,159 --> 00:50:17,860
[SPEAKER_00] na nešto veće,

818
00:50:17,860 --> 00:50:21,480
[SPEAKER_00] zbog toga jer smo htjeli štedjet za nešto veće,

819
00:50:21,480 --> 00:50:24,400
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno za jednog dana našu vlastitu kuću.

820
00:50:24,920 --> 00:50:25,840
[SPEAKER_00] I tako došlo je prvo djete,

821
00:50:25,840 --> 00:50:26,659
[SPEAKER_00] došlo je drugo djete

822
00:50:26,659 --> 00:50:29,139
[SPEAKER_00] i nadje smo ostali u tih dvadesetak kvadrata.

823
00:50:29,139 --> 00:50:30,940
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto vam to govorim?

824
00:50:30,940 --> 00:50:32,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, više nisam,

825
00:50:32,739 --> 00:50:34,099
[SPEAKER_00] ali zašto vam to govorim?

826
00:50:34,099 --> 00:50:36,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ali dolazi treće, pa zato.

827
00:50:37,599 --> 00:50:38,619
[SPEAKER_00] Trenutna odgoda

828
00:50:38,619 --> 00:50:43,920
[SPEAKER_00] dovodi do većeg zadovoljstva kasnije.

829
00:50:43,920 --> 00:50:46,760
[SPEAKER_00] Bićete puno zadovoljni

830
00:50:46,760 --> 00:50:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] ako nešto što vam se na prvu svidi,

831
00:50:50,000 --> 00:50:51,960
[SPEAKER_00] ali ponavljam,

832
00:50:51,960 --> 00:50:54,219
[SPEAKER_00] nije potreba, želja je, preferencija.

833
00:50:54,219 --> 00:50:56,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ako to prvo prezrete,

834
00:50:56,760 --> 00:51:00,280
[SPEAKER_00] znači mora vam se doći do te granice

835
00:51:00,280 --> 00:51:01,079
[SPEAKER_00] da vam se zgadi

836
00:51:01,079 --> 00:51:03,039
[SPEAKER_00] i onda to kupite.

837
00:51:06,360 --> 00:51:08,059
[SPEAKER_00] Osjećate puno veće zadovoljstva.

838
00:51:08,059 --> 00:51:15,659
[SPEAKER_00] Filipljani 4.9 kaže

839
00:51:15,659 --> 00:51:17,940
[SPEAKER_00] Što ste naučili, primili i čuli

840
00:51:17,940 --> 00:51:19,179
[SPEAKER_00] i vidjeli na meni,

841
00:51:19,179 --> 00:51:22,019
[SPEAKER_00] to činite i Bog mira bit će s vama.

842
00:51:22,019 --> 00:51:28,940
[SPEAKER_00] Šmo još ukratko samo.

843
00:51:28,940 --> 00:51:32,260
[SPEAKER_00] Preskočit ću ovo jedan dio,

844
00:51:32,260 --> 00:51:34,179
[SPEAKER_00] ali evo, volio bi još samo malo

845
00:51:34,179 --> 00:51:37,079
[SPEAKER_00] da raštlanimo pojam davanja.

846
00:51:37,079 --> 00:51:39,159
[SPEAKER_00] Davanje kao takvo.

847
00:51:39,159 --> 00:51:41,639
[SPEAKER_00] Koje su prednosti davanja?

848
00:51:43,480 --> 00:51:46,039
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno, svaki dar pomaže potrebitima,

849
00:51:46,039 --> 00:51:48,460
[SPEAKER_00] ali u Božem ekonomskom sustavu

850
00:51:48,460 --> 00:51:51,780
[SPEAKER_00] blagoslov koji doživljava darivatelj

851
00:51:51,780 --> 00:51:54,119
[SPEAKER_00] i koji daje iz ispravnih pobuda,

852
00:51:54,119 --> 00:51:59,219
[SPEAKER_00] veći je nego blagoslov koji prima sam,

853
00:51:59,219 --> 00:52:02,119
[SPEAKER_00] jer milodar, odnosno primatelj tog dara.

854
00:52:02,119 --> 00:52:03,340
[SPEAKER_00] Jeste razumijeli?

855
00:52:03,340 --> 00:52:05,199
[SPEAKER_00] Blaženije je davati nego primati.

856
00:52:05,199 --> 00:52:06,960
[SPEAKER_00] Dijela apostolska.

857
00:52:08,920 --> 00:52:11,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što vas vjerojatno zanima je koliko trebamo davati.

858
00:52:11,500 --> 00:52:14,360
[SPEAKER_00] A koliko vam srce želi?

859
00:52:14,360 --> 00:52:18,900
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, ovaj,

860
00:52:21,559 --> 00:52:23,199
[SPEAKER_00] Bog voli vesela darivatelja.

861
00:52:23,199 --> 00:52:25,400
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da je, evo,

862
00:52:25,400 --> 00:52:27,039
[SPEAKER_00] moja preporuka neka je da

863
00:52:27,039 --> 00:52:29,079
[SPEAKER_00] desetina treba biti tek minimum.

864
00:52:33,219 --> 00:52:34,619
[SPEAKER_00] Pogotovo za Božje stvari.

865
00:52:34,619 --> 00:52:36,500
[SPEAKER_00] Tek minimum.

866
00:52:36,500 --> 00:52:39,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ali,

867
00:52:39,880 --> 00:52:42,659
[SPEAKER_00] na svako treba se najprije

868
00:52:42,659 --> 00:52:43,900
[SPEAKER_00] u potpunosti predati Bogu

869
00:52:43,900 --> 00:52:46,619
[SPEAKER_00] i iskreno tražiti njegovu volju u tomu svemu.

870
00:52:46,619 --> 00:52:50,219
[SPEAKER_00] Kada trebamo davati,

871
00:52:50,219 --> 00:52:51,900
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno kako trebamo davati, pardon?

872
00:52:51,900 --> 00:52:54,340
[SPEAKER_00] Osobno,

873
00:52:54,340 --> 00:52:56,380
[SPEAKER_00] znači svako pono osobda da,

874
00:52:56,380 --> 00:52:58,219
[SPEAKER_00] treba davati redovito

875
00:52:58,219 --> 00:53:00,440
[SPEAKER_00] da ne bi izgubili taj ciklus.

876
00:53:01,059 --> 00:53:03,300
[SPEAKER_00] jer ima nas koji kažemo,

877
00:53:03,300 --> 00:53:04,360
[SPEAKER_00] a, dobro, stavit ću sa strane,

878
00:53:04,360 --> 00:53:05,039
[SPEAKER_00] pa ću da to.

879
00:53:05,039 --> 00:53:06,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vam kažem,

880
00:53:06,739 --> 00:53:08,320
[SPEAKER_00] sto potpunosti izgubite se u računici

881
00:53:08,320 --> 00:53:09,179
[SPEAKER_00] nakon mjeseci i po.

882
00:53:09,179 --> 00:53:13,739
[SPEAKER_00] I trebamo davati

883
00:53:13,739 --> 00:53:14,860
[SPEAKER_00] što smo ranije odvojili.

884
00:53:14,860 --> 00:53:15,619
[SPEAKER_00] A kako ćemo,

885
00:53:15,619 --> 00:53:17,239
[SPEAKER_00] ako ne znamo koliko smo ranije odvojili,

886
00:53:17,239 --> 00:53:17,880
[SPEAKER_00] ako je to negdje,

887
00:53:17,880 --> 00:53:18,360
[SPEAKER_00] aha, ajde,

888
00:53:18,360 --> 00:53:19,820
[SPEAKER_00] pocuknut ću samo za ovo,

889
00:53:19,820 --> 00:53:21,059
[SPEAKER_00] pa ajde još ovo,

890
00:53:21,059 --> 00:53:22,820
[SPEAKER_00] pa i tako ovde ta desetina

891
00:53:22,820 --> 00:53:24,400
[SPEAKER_00] koju smo navodno spremili.

892
00:53:24,400 --> 00:53:28,400
[SPEAKER_00] I trebamo davati razmišljajući,

893
00:53:28,400 --> 00:53:30,039
[SPEAKER_00] razmišljajući

894
00:53:30,039 --> 00:53:31,420
[SPEAKER_00] koliko treba davati.

895
00:53:31,420 --> 00:53:33,800
[SPEAKER_00] Kome treba davati?

896
00:53:33,800 --> 00:53:36,579
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, tu možemo staviti obitelj,

897
00:53:36,579 --> 00:53:38,019
[SPEAKER_00] našu zajednicu,

898
00:53:38,019 --> 00:53:40,019
[SPEAKER_00] misije, službe siromašne.

899
00:53:40,019 --> 00:53:43,400
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, kako god je gospodnja volja,

900
00:53:43,400 --> 00:53:44,860
[SPEAKER_00] iako smo mi u Bogu

901
00:53:44,860 --> 00:53:46,119
[SPEAKER_00] i bogatimo se o Bogu,

902
00:53:46,119 --> 00:53:48,780
[SPEAKER_00] znaćemo na koju adresu treba postati

903
00:53:48,780 --> 00:53:50,059
[SPEAKER_00] ili kome treba taj novac.

904
00:53:50,059 --> 00:53:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tu bih volio izdvojiti,

905
00:53:53,000 --> 00:53:57,579
[SPEAKER_00] i ovo će biti jedno moje osobno razmišljanje,

906
00:53:57,579 --> 00:54:00,019
[SPEAKER_00] iako ću se poslužiti biblijskim citatima.

907
00:54:00,019 --> 00:54:01,380
[SPEAKER_00] Gledajte,

908
00:54:01,900 --> 00:54:02,940
[SPEAKER_00] Prva Timoteo kaže,

909
00:54:02,940 --> 00:54:04,079
[SPEAKER_00] starješine,

910
00:54:04,079 --> 00:54:06,019
[SPEAKER_00] koji su dobri predstojnici,

911
00:54:06,019 --> 00:54:08,440
[SPEAKER_00] dostojni su dvostruke časti,

912
00:54:08,440 --> 00:54:13,119
[SPEAKER_00] pone prije oni koji se trude oko riječi i poučavanja.

913
00:54:14,440 --> 00:54:16,199
[SPEAKER_00] I Galačani 6.6. kaže,

914
00:54:16,199 --> 00:54:18,239
[SPEAKER_00] koji se uči riječi,

915
00:54:18,239 --> 00:54:19,579
[SPEAKER_00] to ste svi vi,

916
00:54:19,579 --> 00:54:22,739
[SPEAKER_00] neka sva dobra dijeli sa svojim učiteljem.

917
00:54:22,739 --> 00:54:27,420
[SPEAKER_00] Malo sam osnovan ovdje,

918
00:54:27,420 --> 00:54:34,539
[SPEAKER_00] zato što neki smatraju da vrijeme stvaranja pouke je malo.

919
00:54:34,539 --> 00:54:36,639
[SPEAKER_00] Neki smatraju da, ne znam,

920
00:54:36,639 --> 00:54:41,559
[SPEAKER_00] kažem, Matija ili Mišo ili neko kogod ovdje poučava riječ,

921
00:54:41,559 --> 00:54:42,920
[SPEAKER_00] misli da to napravi ovako.

922
00:54:44,239 --> 00:54:45,219
[SPEAKER_00] Za to treba vremena.

923
00:54:45,219 --> 00:54:48,079
[SPEAKER_00] Znate onu staru poslovicu.

924
00:54:48,079 --> 00:54:50,219
[SPEAKER_00] Vrijeme je...

925
00:54:50,219 --> 00:54:52,599
[SPEAKER_00] Vrijeme je novac.

926
00:54:52,599 --> 00:54:54,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ali neću završit s tim.

927
00:54:54,699 --> 00:54:57,400
[SPEAKER_00] Neću završit s tim.

